snippet.title: Manic Karts gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Manic Karts, Dos PC game produced by Virgin Interactive in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/manic-karts/7047/
Manic Karts is an interesting game, racing, made in the mid 90's.They're racing karts with different tracks quite interesting.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
